Speaking with stakeholders to understand their primary needs. You have to operate effectively and autonomously across multiple teams in situations of ambiguity, with only high-level direction;
Perform exploratory analyzes;
Build data pipelines applying business logic, choosing levels of aggregation, grouping and transforming fields, checking data quality, and cleaning data;
Maintain and advocate code and pipeline standards through code review, including testing, documentation, and reproducibility;
Build robust data models and ensure they are running reliably in a production environment.

